      "content": "but it's not just about my mistakes. it's about the energy. they're always walking on eggshells around me, always worried about how i'm doing or what's next. if i was just... gone... they wouldn't have to worry anymore. wouldn't they be better off just having the peace? it almost feels like the only way i can actually be good for them is to not be a part of their lives anymore.",
